Package: samplingin
Title: Package for Survey Sampling
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Choerul", "Afifanto", , "choerulafifanto@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Survey Sampling using specified method. Currently utilizing two methods, Systematic and Probability Proportional to Size (PPS) sampling without replacement. Allocate predetermined allocations to smaller levels.
